RESILIENCE

Plan & Let Go

We're going to explore action planning shortly, but in a nutshell - resilient people have learnt that to really 'Let it Go' they need to do four key things:

Dont dwell

Deal with the here and now

Plan and prepare

Reflect

1: Don't dwell on an issue

Reflect on it, understand it and move on, don't keep repeating the thought.

2: Deal with the here and now

Look at the issue you're facing right now and describe what needs to be resolved.

3. Plan and prepare your action

What will your response be, what do you need to do and how will you do this.

4: Reflect

Now step back from the issue and take a fresh, objective look at the whole thing, tweaking your action where appropriate.
